tough%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%20make%20your%20product%20in%20America%20and%20we%20will%20give%20you%20among%20the%20lowest%20taxes%20of%20any%20nation%20on%20earth%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20don't%20make%20your%20product%20in%20America%2C%20which%20is%20your%20prerogative%2C%20then%20very%20simply%20you%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20tariff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20wide-ranging%20speech%2C%20Trump%20made%20a%20link%20between%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20oil%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20he%20would%20ask%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20the%20Organization%20of%20the%20Petroleum%20Exporting%20Countries%20to%20bring%20down%20crude%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20price%20came%20down%2C%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20would%20end%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20had%20a%20message%20for%20central%20banks%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bdemand%20that%20interest%20rates%20drop%20immediately%26quot%3B%20--%20in%20a%20signal%20that%20he%20might%20pressure%20the%20independent%20US%20Federal%20Reserve%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20leader%20then%20fielded%20questions%20from%20four%20top%20banking%20and%20energy%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20Mr.%20president%2C%20I'm%20sure%20the%20crown%20prince%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%20will%20be%20really%20glad%20you%20gave%20this%20speech%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20quipped%20Stephen%20Schwarzman%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20Blackstone%20investment%20firm%2C%20who%20had%20the%20first%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20answered%20the%20group%20one%20by%20one%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20praise%2C%20promises%20and%20reprimand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20make%20a%20deal%2C%20we%20make%20a%20deal.%20You'll%20get%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20after%20the%20head%20of%20French%20energy%20giant%20TotalEnergies%20Patr