A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F227-brad-hogg-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBrad%20Hogg%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20star%20India%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E's%20poor%20performance%20in%20recent%20times%20could%20be%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bdrama%20off%20the%20field%26quot%3B%20more%20than%20things%20happening%20on%20the%20field%20and%20added%20that%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)'s%20new%20policy%20on%20families%20during%20international%20tours%20could%20put%20more%20stress%20on%20the%20veteran%20batter.%20Virat%2C%20who%20could%20just%20make%20190%20runs%20in%2010%20innings%20during%20the%20recently-concluded%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20was%20among%20players%20who%20came%20under%20scrutiny%20after%20the%201-3%20series%20loss%20to%20Australia.%20Virat%20ended%20the%20last%20year%20with%20just%20655%20international%20runs%20in%2023%20matches%20and%2032%20innings%2C%20averaging%2021.83%2C%20with%20a%20century%20and%20two%20fifties%20to%20his%20name.%20His%20best%20score%20was%20100*.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20team's%20collective%20failure%2C%20BCCI%20introduced%20a%20new%20policy%20for%20players%2C%20touching%20on%20several%20aspects%20like%20luggage%2C%20family%20involvement%20in%20tours%2C%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%20etc.%20As%20per%20the%20new%20policy%2C%20the%20player's%20family%20time%20during%20away%20tours%20has%20been%20restricted%20to%20just%2014%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Hogg%2C%20member%20of%20Australia's%202003%20and%202007%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20sqiad%2C%20said%20that%20Virat%20has%20%26quot%3Btoo%20much%20on%20his%20plate%26quot%3B%20right%20now%20which%20has%20caused%20him%20to%20not%20play%20at%20his%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20got%20a%20family%20now.%20He%20has%20other%20commitments%20off%20the%20field%20that%20he%20did%20not%20have%20when%20he%20was%20really%20dominating%20all%20three%20formats%20around%20the%20globe.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20about%20the%20cricket%2C%20it%20is%20what%20happening%20off%20the%20field%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hogg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20more%20the%20drama%20off-field%20than%20on-field%20for%20Virat.%20I%20just%20think%20he%20has%20just%20got%20too%20much%20on%20his%20plate%20that%20has%20probably%20caused%20him%20to%20not%20perform%20as%20well%20at%20this%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20further%20on%20BCCI's%20rules%20about%20families%2C%20Hogg%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20new%20rules%20that%20the%20BCCI%20have%20brought%20in%20in%20regards%20to%20families%2C%20that's%20even%20going%20to%20put%20more%20stress%20on%20Virat%2C%20for%20his%20wife%20and%20family%20as%20well%20because%20you%20got%20to%20have%20that%20balance.%20I%20think%20players%20should%20be%20able%20to%20have%20their%20families%20on%20tour%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20cricket%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20travel%20that%20India%20has%20at%20the%20present%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHogg%20also%20said%20that%20India's%20problems%20during%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20were%20not%20due%20to%20their%20families%20being%20around%2C%20but%20rather%20it%20was%20about%20the%20culture%20built%20by%20the%20new%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20support%20staff%20in%20the%20dressing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20massive%20decline%20in%20his%20Test%20performances%20that%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20start%20of%202020.%20In%2039%20Test%20matches%20since%20the%20start%20of%202020%2C%20Virat%20has%20scored%20jus