speech-apple-meta-bank-of-america-tariffs-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20appeared%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Switzerland%20to%20give%20a%20speech.%20During%20his%20speech%2C%20which%20also%20covered%20topics%20such%20as%20tariffs%20and%20inflation%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bdemand%20that%20interest%20rates%20drop%20immediately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20interest%20rate%20drops%20are%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%20certificates%20of%20deposit%20are%20a%20great%20way%20to%20lock%20in%20a%20good%20rate%20before%20rates%20lower.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fwho-has-the-best-cd-rates-right-now%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20CD%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20between%204.50%25%20and%205.00%25%20APY%2C%20and%20once%20you%20open%20a%20CD%2C%20you'll%20be%20locked%20into%20that%20rate%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20its%20term%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc334461-d12b-425d-a27e-b4ef5076b9dc%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20prepare%20for%20lower%20CD%20rates%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%20which%20is%20the%20central%20banking%20system%20of%20the%20U.S.%2C%20can%20greatly%20impact%20interest%20rates%20by%20raising%20or%20lowering%20the%20federal%20funds%20rate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fwhen-is-the-next-fed-meeting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhen%20the%20next%20Federal%20Reserve%20meeting%20takes%20place%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20President%2C%20Trump%20cannot%20require%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20to%20raise%20or%20lower%20its%20rates%20since%20the%20Fed%20acts%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20from%20the%20presidential%20branch%20is%20that%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20is%20the%20one%20who%20ultimately%20makes%20these%20decisions.%20We've%20never%20seen%20a%20president%20be%20able%20to%20unilaterally%20sway%20what%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20has%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Christopher%20Stroup%2C%20CFP%C2%AE%20professional%2C%20founder%20and%20financial%20advisor%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.siliconbeachplanning.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Beach%20Financial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve's%20decisions%20on%20whether%20to%20raise%20or%20lower%20rates%20depend%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20economy.%20%26quot%3BPrice%20stability%20and%20full%20employment%20is%20the%20dual%20mandate%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Stuart%20Schiffman%2C%20CFP%C2%AE%20professional%2C%20managing%20partner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcwealthadvisor.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECompound%20Wealth%20Advisors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-rate-cuts-federal-reserve-final-decision-powell-trump-inflation-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve%20lowered%20rates%20in%20December%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%202024%20after%20lowering%20interest%20rates%20in%20September%20and%20October%20before%20that.%20But%20it%20might%20not%20continue%20that%20trend%20in%20the%20new%20year%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmegroup.com%2Fmarkets%2Finterest-rates%2Fcme-fedwatch-tool.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECME%20Fedwatch%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%20predicts%20an%20over%2090%25%20chance%20that%20the%20federal%20funds%20rate%20will%20stay%20the%20same%20at%20the%20January%2028%20to%2029%20Federal%20Reserve%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Federal%20Reserve%20indicated%20that%20they%20were%20going%20to%20slow%20the%20drop-down%20in%20interest%20rates%20so%20that%20they%20could%20gather%20more%20information%20around%20what%20was%20happening%20with%20inflation%20and%20also%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%2