toc-id%3D%5C%22c8d8afe8-1479-4ff6-b899-e1efa57889e7%5C%22%3EA%20young%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20the%20world's%20largest%20bank%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20indictment%20against%20them%2C%20Javice%20and%20Amar%20together%20conned%20the%20nation's%20largest%20bank%20into%20paying%20a%20small%20fortune%20for%20Frank%2C%20a%20for-profit%20tech%20company%20she%20launched%20at%20age%2024%20that%20featured%20software%20to%20help%20students%20apply%20for%20college%20financial%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%20began%20wooing%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202021.%20Then%2028%2C%20Javice%20was%20something%20of%20a%20media%20darling%2C%20giving%20interviews%20to%20major%20news%20publications%20and%20making%20not%20only%20the%20Forbes%20list%2C%20but%20the%20Crain's%20New%20York's%2040%20under%2040%20list%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20wait%20for%20the%20time%20to%20move%20up%20the%20ranks%20in%20the%20traditional%20sense%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20negotiation%2C%20Javice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F28-founder-ceo-frank-financial-aid-leadership-tactics-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%202021.%20That%20was%20the%20same%20month%20that%20prosecutors%20say%20she%20gave%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20with%20two%20Power%20Point%20presentations%20alleging%20Frank%20had%20more%20than%204%20million%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20an%20opportunity%2C%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20jump%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20these%20claims%20of%20a%20massive%20user%20base%20that%20lured%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20in.%20The%20bank%20acquired%20Frank%2C%20in%20large%20part%2C%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20these%20users%2C%20hoping%20that%20these%20up-and-coming%20college%20students%20would%20become%20new%20customers%20for%20Chase%20products%2C%20federal%20prosecutors%20say%20in%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20bank%20asked%20to%20verify%20Frank's%20user%20database%20before%20committing%20to%20the%20acquisition%2C%20Javice%20and%20Amar%20called%20up%20their%20director%20of%20software%20engineering.%20They%20asked%20the%20engineer%20to%20create%20synthetic%20data%20that%20would%20make%20it%20look%20like%20they%20had%20millions%20of%20users%2C%20prosecutors%20allege.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20it's%20legal%2C%26quot%3B%20Amar%20allegedly%20told%20the%20engineer%20in%20a%20message%20cited%20by%20prosecutors.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20to%20end%20up%20in%20orange%20jumpsuits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20engineer%20balked.%20So%20the%20pair%20paid%20%2418%2C000%20to%20an%20outside%20data%20scientist%20who%20generated%20what%20prosecutors%20say%20were%204%20million%20rows%20of%20utterly%20fabricated%20names%2C%20emails%2C%20home%20addresses%2C%20and%20phone%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20defendants%20created%20a%20fake%20dataset%2C%26quot%3B%20Assistant%20US%20Attorney%20Micah%20Festa%20Fergenson%20said%20at%20Amar's%20arraignment%20in%20July.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20essentially%20a%20giant%20Excel%20spreadsheet%20that%20had%20over%204%20million%20rows%20and%20lots%20of%20purported%20data.%20But%20it%20was%20all%20fake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20went%20through%20in%20September%202021%2C%20with%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20keeping%20Javice%20and%20Amar%20on%20as%20Frank's%20No.%201%20and%20No.%202.%20As%20JPMorgan%20Chase's%20new%20head%20of%20student%20solutions%2C%20Javice%20was%20paid%20a%20%24300%2C000%20annual%20salary%20and%20pocketed%20%2421%20million%20in%20stock%20proceeds%20plus%20a%20%2420%20million%20retention%20bonus%2C%20prosecutors%20allege.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20the%20bank%20would%20soon%20try%20to%20use%20the%20data%20to%20pitch%20savings%20accounts%2C%20credit%20cards%2C%20and%20the%20like%2C%20the%20pair%20then%20purchased%2C%20for%20%24100%2C000%20on%20the%20open%20market%2C%20the%20data%20for%20more%20than%20four%20million%20college%20students%2C%20prosecutors%20allege.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Chase%20eventually%20went%20and%20asked%20them%2C%20%26quot%3BOkay%2C%20send%20your%20student%20data%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20sent%20this%20student%20list%20that%20they%20had%20bought%20on%20the%20open%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Fergenson%20alleged%20at%20Amar's%20arraignment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20year%20after%20the%20sale%20did%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20realize%20that%20Frank%20had%20no%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20legitimate%20user%20contacts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%204%20million%20contacts%20were%20essentially%20worthless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChase%20did%20a%20test%20run%20of%20a%20marketing%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prosecutor%20said%20at%20Amar's%20arraignment.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20emails%20were%20old%20and%20didn't%20work.%20Almost%20nobody%20clicked%20through%20to%20it.%20And%20it%20was%20completely%20unexpected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20shut%20Frank%20down%2C%20firing%20and%20suing%20Javice.%20She%20was%20arrested%20in%20April%202023%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20three%20months%20later.%20Both%20have%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20charges%20of%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20securities%2C%20wire%2C%20and%20bank%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%20is%20free%20on%20%242%20million%20bail%2C%20which%20was%20secured%20by%20her%20home%20in%20Miami%20Beach.%20Amar%20is%20out%20on%20%241%20million%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice's%20lawyers%20have%20argued%20that%20the%20materials%20sent%20to%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20during%20the%202021%20sale%20negotiations%20were%20legally%20obtained%20and%20did%20not%20constitute%20fraud%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20the%20government's%20case%20simply%20piggybacks%20on%20the%20bank's%20December%202022%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmar's%20lawyers%20have%20said%20that%20he%20was%20at%20arm's%20length%20from%20the%20sale%20itself%20and%20that%20he%20did%20not%20knowingly%20participate%20in%20any%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20Charlie%20Javice%20walking.%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65296aba55f52b01b35f128f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharlie%20Javice%20arriving%20at%20Federal%20Court.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Minchillo%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d85c6b56-796d-4515-88a1-bd85e8e29878%5C%22%3EA%20last-minute%20evidence%20dump%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20original%20date%20for%20jury%20selection%20%E2%80%94%20the%20second%20Monday%20in%20February%20%E2%80%94%20was%20pushed%20forward%20a%20week%20to%20February%2018.%20The%20judge%20moved%20the%20date%20to%20give%20the%20defendants%20more%20time%20to%20process%20an%20emergency%2C%20last-minute%20evidence%20dump%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20snafu%20to%20the%20judge%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20that%2014%20months%20ago%2C%20back%20in%20October%202023%2C%20they%20received%20two%20large%20caches%20of%20data%20in%20response%20to%20a%20subpoena%20to%20Google%3A%20all%20of%20Javice's%20Google%20Drive%20documents%20and%20all%20of%20Amar's%20Google%20Drive%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20immediately%20shared%20Javice's%20drive%20documents%20to%20her%20defense%20team%2C%20and%20all%20of%20Amar's%20drive%20documents%20to%20his%20team%20%E2%80%94%20a%20total%20of%2013%2C000%20documents%20%E2%80%94%20as%20required%20under%20federal%20rules%20of%20evidence.%20But%20they%20neglected%20to%20give%20Javice's%20documents%20to%20Amar%2C%20and%20vice-versa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20would%20you%20like%20to%20get%2013%2C000%20documents%20two%20weeks%20before%20trial%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20demanded%20angrily.%20%26quot%3BHow%20did%20that%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20remains%20in%20the%20dark%20on%20what%20Amar's%20%26quot%3Bderogation%26quot%3B%20defense%2