%20thinner%20skin%2C%20like%20the%20undereye%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20necessarily%20need%20to%20choose%20a%20thicker%20foundation%20to%20achieve%20a%20full-coverage%20finish%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20makeup%20artist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Frdkmakeup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaria%20I.%20Rincon%20Djuro%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20KIKO%20Milano%20Full%20Coverage%202-in-1%20Foundation%20and%20Concealer%20is%20amazing%20at%20hiding%20blemishes%2C%20under-eye%20circles%2C%20discoloration%2C%20and%20fine%20lines!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229bf0f7c6-07bf-437f-93e8-32d98b4c18c5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20luxury%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20author%20wearing%20the%20La%20Mer%20The%20Soft%20Fluid%20Long%20Wear%20Foundation%20and%20their%20hand%20holding%20the%20bottle%20side%20by%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679176d7ae09223df2bb2441%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENeha%20Tandon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20one%20makeup%20product%20you%20should%20splurge%20on%2C%20it's%20foundation.%20Whether%20you%20have%20fine%20lines%20you%20want%20to%20soften%2C%20want%20more%20plump-looking%20skin%2C%20or%20are%20simply%20craving%20a%20more%20blurred%20%E2%80%94%20yet%20natural-looking%20%E2%80%94%20appearance%20to%20your%20skin%2C%20the%20La%20Mer%20foundation%20is%20here%20to%20provide%20medium-to-full%20coverage%20while%20helping%20to%20treat%20the%20skin.%20It%20contains%20a%20blend%20of%20oils%2C%20fruit%20extracts%2C%20SPF%2020%2C%20and%20the%20brand's%20iconic%20Miracle%20Broth.%20The%20latter%20is%20La%20Mer's%20patented%20blend%20of%20giant%20sea%20kelp%2C%20vitamins%2C%20and%20minerals%20that%20have%20been%20fermented%20to%20help%20fortify%20the%20skin%2C%20making%20this%20a%20true%20treat%20for%20your%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20a%20water-like%20consistency%20with%20medium%2C%20buildable%20coverage%20that's%20ideal%20for%20daily%20wear%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20natural%20finish.%20I%20love%20that%20I'm%20getting%20the%20benefits%20of%20La%20Mer's%20potent%20and%20beloved%20skincare%20and%20coverage.%20I'll%20just%20use%20a%20small%20half%20of%20a%20pump%20for%20daily%20wear%2C%20and%20then%20I%20use%20one%20to%20two%20pumps%20when%20I%20want%20a%20full-coverage%20look.%20I%20love%20how%20lightweight%20it%20feels%20and%20that%20it%20evens%20out%20my%20hyperpigmentation%20without%20feeling%20or%20looking%20like%20I%20have%20much%20on%20my%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd40bf2d-37fc-4c1b-aeda-ea5ff39c9dfa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20natural%20finish%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20your%20skin%20type%2C%20a%20natural%20finish%20will%20always%20do.%20This%20versatile%20pick%20from%20Bobbi%20Brown%20has%20that%2C%20and%20it's%20also%20blended%20with%20SPF%2015%2C%20vitamin%20C%2C%20and%20hyaluronic%20acid.%20The%20creamy%20formula%20feels%20just%20like%20a%20moisturizer%2C%20but%20its%20tint%20helps%20to%20blur%20the%20appearance%20of%20pores%20softly%20for%20a%20natural%20and%20slightly%20glowy%20finish.%20It%20even%20contains%20shea%20butter%2C%20which%20helps%20to%20keep%20this%20from%20settling%20into%20fine%20lines%20after%20hours%20of%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20has%20loved%20this%20foundation%20for%20years%2C%20and%20I%20finally%20tried%20it%20myself%20recently.%20While%20it's%20labeled%20as%20a%20light%20coverage%20tint%2C%20I%20feel%20this%20is%20much%20more%20of%20a%20medium-to-full%20coverage%20formula%20(as%20does%20my%20mother).%20It%20totally%20fills%20in%20the%20large%20pores%20I%20have%20on%20my%20cheeks%20and%20blurs%20the%20appearance%20of%20the%20hyperpigmentation%20I%20have%20on%20my%20jawline%2C%20giving%20me%20an%20overall%20softer%20look%20that%20doesn't%20actually%20%3Cem%3Elook%3C%2Fem%3E%20like%20I'm%20wearing%20makeup.%20Plus%2C%20the%20ultra-moisturizing%20formula%20gives%20my%20dry%20skin%20a%20slightly%20satiny%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2242f73dcf-b530-4b80-a7b8-a9ee4629fd55%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20foundation%20stick%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20smooth%20texture%20and%20natural%20finish%2C%20this%20stick%20foundation%20from%20cruelty-free%20brand%20Well%20People%20contains%20ingredients%20that%20will%20manage%20oil%20production%20while%20helping%20to%20prevent%20acne%20and%20nourish%20the%20skin.%20A%20fitting%20choice%20for%20any%20skin%20type%2C%20the%20fragrance-free%20formula%20is%20also%20suitable%20for%20sensitive%20skin%20types.%20Black%20seed%20oil%20helps%20to%20soothe%20redness%2C%20acne%2C%20eczema%2C%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20inflammation%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20dry%20skin%20along%20with%20hyperpigmentation%20that%20can%20be%20really%20hard%20to%20cover%20up.%20I%20love%20that%20this%20has%20a%20natural%20finish%2C%20so%20I%20can%20use%20it%20for%20targeted%20application%20on%20any%20acne%20scars%2C%20dark%20circles%2C%20or%20any%20other%20spots%20I%20have.%20The%20stick%20format%20makes%20precise%20application%20super%20easy%2C%20and%20I%20love%20that%20this%20has%20a%20creamy%20feel%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285a9ea48-2fd9-4966-b78f-40a851d65ee8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20matte%20finish%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20author%20wearing%20the%20Valentino%20Very%20Valentino%2024-Hour%20Long-Wear%20Liquid%20Foundation%20and%20their%20hand%20holding%20the%20bottle%20side%20by%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679272e82fcded5e907479b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENeha%20Tandon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20matte%20foundations%20are%20notorious%20for%20settling%20into%20fine%20lines%20and%20drying%20out%20skin%2C%20Valentino's%20Very%20Valentino%2024-Hour%20Long-Wear%20Liquid%20Foundation%20contains%20glycerin%20and%20bergamot%20fruit%20oil%20to%20hydrate%20skin%20while%20calming%20inflammation%20lightly.%20The%20lightweight%20liquid%20dries%20to%20a%20powder-like%20finish%20upon%20application%2C%20so%20be%20sure%20to%20blend%20it%20quickly.%20The%20lightweight%20and%20breathable%20formula%20gives%20skin%20a%20matte%20look%2C%20so%20you'll%20love%20using%20it%20as%20a%20base%20for%20a%20fully%20matte%20look%20or%20to%20put%20layers%20of%20highlighter%20or%20bronzer%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20my%20go-to%20for%20the%20longest%20days%20I%20have.%20It's%20perfect%20for%20weddings%20when%20I'll%20be%20at%20a%20ceremony%20in%20the%20morning%20followed%20by%20a%20lunch%2C%20reception%2C%20and%20after%20party.%20I%20can%20always%20count%20on%20this%20to%20stay%20put%20without%20any%20primer%2C%20setting%20powder%2C%20or%20setting%20spray%20necessary.%20I%20worry%20about%20how%20matte%20foundations%20will%20amplify%20the%20dryness%20in%20my%20already-dry%20skin%2C%20but%20this%20just%20creates%20a%20soft%2C%20velvety-looking%20veil%20across%20my%20skin%20and%20creates%20a%20solid%20first%20layer%20for%20me%20to%20layer%20liquid%20and%20powder%20highlighters%20on%20top%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294366927-3573-4f74-9edc-5b357b1952ef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20satin%20finish%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20author%20wearing%20the%20Charlotte%20Tilbury%20Beautiful%20Skin%20Foundation%20and%20their%20hand%20holding%20the%20bottle%20side%20by%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6788316de294a7514e8d5f0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ENeha%20Tandon%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20the%20Charlotte%20Tilbury%20Beautiful%20Skin%20Foundation%20costs%20%2449%20for%20a%20hand-sized%20tube%2C%20but%20it%20is%20worth%20it%20if%20you%20want%20to%20nail%20that%20classic%20candle-lit%20glow.%20It%20contains%20a%20variety%20of%20nourishing%20ingredients%2C%20like%20hyaluronic%20acid%2C%20coconut%20extract%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20rose%20water%2C%20and%20rose%20oil%2C%20and%20it%20gives%20skin%20a%20natural-looking%20radiance.%20A%20patented%20bix-active%20complex%20also%20reduces%20excess%20shine%20while%20blurring%20the%20look%20of%20pores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20my%20go-to%20for%20nights%20out%20because%20it%20makes%20my%20skin%20look%20so%20glowy%20and%20has%20a%20way%20of%20airbrushing%20right%20over%20the%20large%20pores%20I%20have%20on%20my%20cheeks.%20Usually%2C%20I%20end%20up%20needing%20a%20powder%20of%20some%20sort%20to%20make%20sure%20glowy%20foundations%20don't%20end%20up%20looking%20greasy%20on%20my%20skin%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20end%20up%20needing%20that%20at%20all%20with%20this.%20I%20can%20put%20this%20on%20and%20look%20like%20I%20have%20a%20full%20face%20of%20makeup%20on%2C%20no%20additional%20highlighter%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbb4d6c0-d9d8-4c69-8112-950a404872e5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20dry%20skin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EComplete%20with%20a%20radiant%20finish%20helmed%20by%20a%20lightweight%20liquid%20formula%2C%20housed%20in%20sustainable%20aluminum%20packaging%2C%20this%20is%20jam-packed%20with%20nourishing%2C%20hydrating%20ingredients.%20In%20it%2C%20find%20argan%20oil%2C%20avocado%20oil%2C%20green%20tea%20extract%2C%20hyaluronic%20acid%2C%20and%20more.%20Made%20with%20an%20aloe%20vera%20leaf%20juice%20base%2C%20reviewers%20love%20how%20refreshingly%20light%20the%20formula%20feels%20despite%20how%20hydrating%20it%20feels.%20In%20fact%2C%20Sas%20even%20recommends%20it%20for%20mature%20skin%20because%20it%20won't%20settle%20into%20fine%20lines.%20Even%20Dr.%20Madfes%20recommends%20this%20formula%20to%20her%20clients%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-foundations-for-dry-skin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edry%20skin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20that%20it's%20excellent%20for%20hydration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229418e37b-f44f-40e7-a82e-e57d2ffa3db8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20oily%20skin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20rare%20to%20find%20a%20mattifying%20foundation%20that%20keeps%20oil%20at%20bay%20while%20still%20accentuating%20the%20natural%20contours%20of%20your%20face%20because%20a%20matte%20effect%20can%20sometimes%20also%20equate%20to%20a%20flattening%20effect.%20Infused%20with%20oil-absorbing%20powders%2C%20the%20formula%20leaves%20skin%20looking%20plump%20and%20blurred%20with%20some%20healthy%20dimensions.%20It%20contains%20softening%20glycerin%20to%20make%20sure%20this%20won't%20crease%20on%20your%20skin%2C%20either.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jillmckay.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMakeup%20artist%20Jill%20McKay%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20it's%20one%20of%20her%20favorite%20foundations%20for%20any%20skin%20type%2C%20but%20the%20oil-regulating%20ingredients%20make%20it%20best%20suited%20for%20anyone%20with%20oily%20or%20even%20acne-prone%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9c5f0e8-e8de-4186-b4b6-67b5940e925a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20acne-prone%20skin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlmay's%20Clear%20Complexion%20Foundation%20is%20another%20full-coverage%20foundation%20that%20puts%20skin%20health%20at%20the%20forefront.%20In%20addition%20to%20being%20infused%20with%20salicylic%20acid%20to%20help%20clear%20acne%20while%20covering%20it%2C%20it%20floods%20skin%20with%20antibacterial%20and%20calming%20ingredients%2C%20including%20aloe%20vera%20and%20prebiotics%20to%20ease%20redness%20while%20curbing%20inflammation.%20A%20little%20goes%20a%20long%20way%2C%20so%20you'll%20only%20need%20about%20half%20a%20pump%20to%20cover%20your%20whole%20face%20with%20this%20under-%2420%20option.%20Both%20McKay%20and%20Dr.%20Engelman%20recommend%20this%20formula%20for%20both%20oily%20and%20acne-prone%20skin%20types.%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20help%20regulate%20oil%20production%20without%20compromising%20the%20skin%20barrier%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Engelman.%20%26quot%3BThe%20non-comedogenic%20formula%20keeps%20pores%20clear%20and%20prevents%20clogging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da350caf-1dfb-402a-bad7-fc41874de45e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ingredients%20you%20should%20look%20for%20when%20searching%20for%20a%20full-coverage%20foundation%20will%20depend%20on%20your%20skin%20type.%20Dr.%20Madfes%20says%20that%20people%20with%20dry%20or%20mature%20skin%20should%20look%20for%20shea%20butter%2C%20hyaluronic%20acid%2C%20and%20argan%20oil%2C%20while%20those%20with%20oily%20or%20acne-prone%20skin%20should%20seek%20out%20clay-based%20ingredients%2C%20powders%2C%20and%20silica.%20She%20is%20also%20a%20huge%20proponent%20of%20foundations%20that%20are%20infused%20with%20sun%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETexture%20and%20finish%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatte%20foundations%20give%20skin%20a%20velvety%20look%20made%20with%20ingredients%20that%20won't%20reflect%20light%2C%20while%20dewy%20foundations%20are%20made%20with%20light-reflecting%20particles%20for%20a%20radiant%20finish%20that%20will%20make%20your%20skin%20appear%20more%20plump%20and%20glowy.%20%26quot%3BMatte%20finishes%20suit%20oily%20skin%2C%20while%20satin%20and%20glowy%20finishes%20can%20look%20more%20natural%20on%20drier%20skin%20types%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sas.%20Matte%20foundations%20tend%20to%20last%20a%20bit%20longer%20because%20they're%20made%20with%20oil-absorbing%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShade%20range%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20industry%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20in%20terms%20of%20inclusivity%2C%20which%20is%20why%20many%20brands%20tend%20to%20have%20more%20lighter%20shades%20than%20dark%20ones%2C%20and%20the%20darker%20skin%20tone%20options%20tend%20to%20have%20less%20of%20a%20range%20and%20undertone%20options%20even%20when%20they%20are%20offered.%20Once%20you%20find%20the%20ideal%20shade%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20find%20the%20best%20undertone%20to%20match%20your%20natural%20skin%20tone.%20Look%20at%20your%20veins%20in%20natural%20light.%20If%20they%20appear%20green%2C%20you%20likely%20have%20warm%20undertones.%20If%20they%20appear%20blue%20or%20purple%2C%20you%20likely%20have%20cool%20undertones.%20If%20they%20appear%20blue-green%2C%20chances%20are%20that%20you%20have%20a%20neutral%20undertone.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20darker%20skin%20tone%20like%20I%20do%2C%20chances%20are%20that%20you%20may%20have%20to%20mix%20a%20few%20shades%20to%20get%20your%20exact%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224d13f09-3079-453b-8db0-8062fafc4d16%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFAQs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f4a701f5-9a96-4593-bdcb-baa973939dc3%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20you%20apply%20full-coverage%20foundation%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mades%20says%20that%20the%20best%20way%20to%20apply%20foundation%20is%20with%20freshly%20cleansed%20skin%20right%20on%20top%20of%20your%20SPF%20because%20that'll%20give%20you%20the%20smoothest%20finish.%20After%20that%2C%20the%20way%20you%20apply%20your%20makeup%20will%20depend%20upon%20the%20finish%20you%20desire.%20A%20wet%20sponge%20will%20give%20you%20the%20most%20skin-like%20finish%2C%20while%20fingers%20will%20give%20you%20a%20more%20natural%2C%20lightweight%20coverage%20thanks%20to%20the%20warmth%20in%20your%20fingers.%20Use%20a%20brush%20to%20get%20more%20precise%20control%20and%20fuller%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDjuro%20says%20that%20people%20with%20mature%20skin%20who%20may%20want%20to%20veil%20the%20appearance%20of%20fine%20lines%20can%20add%20one%20extra%20step.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20achieve%20a%20blurred%20look%20by%20using%20a%20silicone%20primer%2C%20waiting%20a%20minute%2C%20and%20then%20applying%20foundation%20for%20a%20blurred%20and%20glowing%20finish%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8e00130-7f26-4144-bdd4-5b3cb80fe789%5C%22%3ECan%20you%20layer%20foundation%20to%20get%20fuller%20coverage%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20%3Cem%3Ecan%3C%2Fem%3E%20you%20layer%20foundation%20to%20get%20fuller%20coverage%2C%20but%20Sas%20says%20that%20you'll%20want%20to%20choose%20a%20buildable%20foundation%20that%20allows%20multiple%20layers.%20%26quot%3BThis%20helps%20avoid%20a%20heavy%2C%20cakey%20look%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20full-coverage%20foundations%20are%20intended%20to%20cover%20everything%20in%20one%20layer%2C%20choose%20one%20that's%20buildable%20for%20flexibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-full-coverage-foundations%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737666953000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6792a9452fcded5e907486a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-full-coverage-foundations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22You%20don't%20have%20to%20sacrifice%20coverage%20for%20radiant%2C%20fresh%20looking%20skin%20with%20the%20best%20full-coverage%20foundations.%20We've%20rounded%20up%20our%20favorites%20from%20Bobbi%20Brown%2C%20Nars%2C%20Makeup%20For%20Ever%2C%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mpascouche%40businessinsider.com%20(Maiya%20Pascouche)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-full-coverage-foundations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20close