20taking%20this%20forward%20by%20giving%20discarded%20plastic%20a%20new%20life.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Sankar%2C%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Senthil%2C%20for%20example%2C%20are%20recycling%20over%2015%20lakh%20bottles%20daily%20through%20their%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20company%2C%20%E2%80%98Shree%20Renga%20Polymers%E2%80%99%2C%20while%20pioneering%20a%20creative%20approach%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F372675%2Fmumbai-designers-prakruthi-rao-akshara-mehta-transforming-fashion-sustainable-textile-juhu-beach-studio%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20fashion%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20their%20clothing%20brand%2C%20%E2%80%98EcoLine%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20they%20do%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20turn%20plastic%20waste%20into%20fashionable%20clothing%2C%20the%20father-son%20duo%20follow%20a%20process%20that%20can%20be%20broadly%20divided%20into%20five%20steps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollection%20and%20sorting%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20PET%20bottles%20are%20collected%20through%20a%20network%20of%2050%2C000%20ragpickers%20across%20states%2C%20including%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Kerala%2C%20and%20Puducherry.%20The%20bottles%20are%20carefully%20sorted%2C%20and%20any%20caps%2C%20wrappers%2C%20or%20contaminants%20are%20removed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrushing%20and%20flaking%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Once%20cleaned%2C%20the%20PET%20bottles%20are%20crushed%20into%20small%20flakes%2C%20typically%20three%20to%20eight%20millimetres%20in%20size.%20This%20step%20reduces%20the%20material%20to%20a%20manageable%20form%20that%20can%20easily%20be%20processed%20into%20new%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMelting%20and%20spinning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20PET%20flakes%20are%20melted%20at%20300%C2%B0C%20using%20an%20extruder.%20The%20molten%20material%20is%20then%20stretched%20to%20form%20polyester%20fibre%2C%20which%20is%20cooled%20and%20transformed%20into%20yarn.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeaving%20the%20fabric%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20yarn%20is%20then%20woven%20into%20fabric%2C%20forming%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20clothing%20line.%20This%20fabric%20is%20then%20tailored%20into%20products%20such%20as%20jackets%2C%20T-shirts%2C%20and%20blazers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaterless%20dyeing%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20One%20of%20the%20key%20innovations%20at%20EcoLine%20is%20the%20use%20of%20dope%20dye%20technology.%20Instead%20of%20dyeing%20the%20fabric%20after%20it%E2%80%99s%20made%20%E2%80%94%20a%20traditional%20process%20that%20consumes%20vast%20amounts%20of%20water%20%E2%80%94%20EcoLine%20infuses%20the%20colour%20directly%20into%20the%20polyester%20fibre%20during%20its%20production.%20This%20unique%20process%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20water%20in%20dyeing%2C%20making%20it%20both%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F313885%2Fhyderabad-manya-cherabuddi-makes-natural-dyes-conducts-workshops-sustainable-living%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20and%20energy-efficient.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCobjzFxv0GJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_emb